PrecisAppointment of NADIA BURGER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, with residence in Jakarta; CAMERON MACKAY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Bhutan, with residence in New Delhi; and CHRISTOPHER THORNLEY as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Rwanda, with residence in Nairobi.
